text: Amjad Ali Khan (), is a Pakistani politician who is member of the National Assembly of Pakistan. ==Political career== Khan won the 2024 Pakistani general election from NA-2 Swat-I as an Independent candidate. He received 88,938 votes while runner up Amir Muqam of Pakistan Muslim League (N) received 37,764 votes. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Pakistani MNAs
